{"tid":1765320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係想食人血饅頭，但想問邊到有援助 對唔住","createTime":"2019-12-01T18:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T20:33:51.000Z","uid":286473,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"51fabef2439f8956888869967e9c362c66b39f13","tid":1765320,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:35:47.000Z","msg":"小弟今年22<br />\n於10.1曾經被捕 之後用左大部份積蓄搵左律師踢保<br />\n612claim左一部分  總之法律野搞好曬<br />\n之後種種更中射波等 整親好咩都好 總之無左份工<br />\n於11月中開始番左新工 但咁岩撞正黎明行動<br />\n唔係好番到 依家都有照常返工 11月住糧要到今個月10號先有<br />\n之後23號同家人吵架左 都係鬧我嗰啲都俾人拉過點解仲要出去等等 比人趕走埋<br />\n加上兩場理大中大戰役消耗左好多<br />\n<br />\n住左一星期荃灣酒店都2xx晚左右 交左租 住到星期三<br />\n屋企人暫時都唔理我<br />\n而家銀包無曬錢曬 得番1百幾十 食飯同酒店開始成問題<br />\n真係唔想食人血饅頭 但想知邊度仲有幫手 <br />\n身邊朋友都已經幫過少少<br />\n對唔住各位"},{"pid":"116304b7f71775281e88f51a55f5816ddba682de","tid":1765320,"uid":303244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:37:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d75798beda23691c272cfa09e3521257b6a79fc","tid":1765320,"uid":141700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:41:46.000Z","msg":"幫推 辛苦曬手足"},{"pid":"4eda2d294fd5c298f1ab1defb90fbe9c7c710abe","tid":1765320,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79f8676daf1417d2d4b20b8805862d7adb0b30d","tid":1765320,"uid":23037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:44:37.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d6663aa44d2614ace3ef9cccb1b8ad019aa45201","tid":1765320,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:44:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5488e22841430cb3e9eb3bba534e6c2bdefce4dd","tid":1765320,"uid":286473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d75798beda23691c272cfa09e3521257b6a79fc","tid":1765320,"uid":141700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:41:46.000Z","msg":"幫推 辛苦曬手足"},"citedBy":0,"re